https://heartbeat.fritz.ai/how-to-build-a-web-app-with-react-native-b93575a16a5e

1) npm install -g create-react-app expo


2) create-react-app myAPpName
    cd into your app ...!!!
3) yarn add --dev babel-plugin-module-resolver

4) yarn add react-native expo react-native-web

//DEV:
yarn start 

//BUILD: 
yarn build
yarn global add serve 
serve -s buildasdf